{
  "description": "A stunning panoramic view of San Francisco during a vibrant sunset. The cityscape, including iconic buildings and skyscrapers, stretches along the bay, bathed in a warm golden light. A long bridge extends into the water, creating a dramatic line. The bay is calm, reflecting the golden hues of the sky and city lights. In the foreground, silhouetted trees and foliage add depth and a natural frame. The sky is a gradient of warm colors, from bright orange near the horizon to softer yellows and oranges higher up. There's a subtle contrast between the illuminated city and the darker waters, highlighting the urban landscape against the natural environment. The overall impression is one of serene beauty and majestic scale.",
